{
  "stem": "10181.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And people were dying from the typhus, you know, because we-- we-- we had lice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had lice all over, you know, slowly but surely.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I think the lice came originally, probably, with the beds, and I'm sure they were in there already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the-- we-- we had no way of getting rid of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you know, lice spread disease.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one of the diseases which were-- which [INAUDIBLE] made Bergen-Belsen so bad was typhus.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, it's-- it's a-- it's a deadly disease.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Many people died or were dying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We-- like I said, we didn't-- I think on my whole stay in Bergen-Belsen, I took two showers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And to take a shower was a-- was a big thing because they had to take us out of the camp to someone else to take a shower.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's why, they-- I guess they never wanted to bother in the first place because in our part of the camp, there were no showers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Anyway, so like I said, things got worse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had this-- continued to have this roll call.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, next to us were people from other camps who had walked into the-- brought into the Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And if they didn't have typhus, they had typhus by the time they got there from us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They got it from us, probably.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they were undernourished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I mean, we were also, of course, undernourished tremendously, but they were even worse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So they died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You know, like, you know, you could see the bodies lying all over the-- all over the camp and piled up in front of the barracks, you know, right to the way roof.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And pits, they dug pits because the crematorium didn't function.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Like I told you before, the crematorium burned down.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
